(7, 1, '2013-03-15 20:27:45', '2013-03-16 01:27:45', '<h2>Angela Holden • Web Designer &amp; Front End Developer</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-730" style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;" alt="Angela J. Holden Website Design" src="http://angelajholden.com/ajh/wp-content/uploads/angela-bio.jpg" width="196" height="228" />\r\n\r\nMy name is Angela Holden and I''m a freelance web designer and technical writer from Minneapolis, MN, now living in San Diego, CA. I love content, color, typography, and providing great user experiences. I''ve been designing websites and producing content for the web for four years and I love every minute that I spend doing it. In 2009 I built my first website, and in 2013 I earned a Master’s Degree in Technical Communication from <a href="http://www.metrostate.edu/msweb/explore/catalog/grad/index.cfm?lvl=G&amp;section=1&amp;page_name=master_science_technical_communication_ms.html" target="_blank">Metropolitan State University</a>.\r\n\r\nI work from my home in San Diego, and have clients in the U.S. and overseas. For more information about what I can do, please visit my <a title="Services" href="http://angelajholden.com/services">services</a> page. If you’d like to see my work, please look at my <a title="Home | Portfolio" href="http://angelajholden.com">portfolio</a>.\r\n\r\nCheers!\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Andrew Davis • Project Manager &amp; Marketing</h2>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-1138" alt="Andrew Parker Davis" src="http://angelajholden.com/ajh/wp-content/uploads/AndrewParkerDavis-200x200.jpg" width="200" height="200" />\r\n\r\nOriginally from San Diego, CA, Andrew Davis’s expertise is project management and marketing. A natural born leader and entrepreneur, he thrives when working with sole proprietors and small business owners on their web design and development projects. He studied at the University of California in La Jolla, and spent five months living in West Africa. He enjoys doing improv and attends technology user groups in San Diego.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<figure><figcaption style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',serif; font-style: italic; text-align: center;">This is where the website magic happens!</figcaption><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1098" alt="Angela J. Holden''s Workspace" src="http://angelajholden.com/ajh/wp-content/uploads/website-workspace.jpg" width="960" height="540" />\r\n\r\n</figure>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2014-02-04 06:12:56', '2014-02-04 12:12:56', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
