(344, 1, '2013-03-29 19:17:53', '2013-03-30 00:17:53', '<h2>How much does it cost to design and build a website?</h2>\r\nIt depends on the project, but usually between $250.00 and $1,000.00. I charge a minimum of $250.00 for website design, so if you don''t need graphics or help with content, we can focus on the website which will keep costs low.\r\n<h2>How much does it cost for graphic design work?</h2>\r\nAgain, it depends on the project. These jobs tend to be unique and I need a fair amount of information about how the work will be used in order to give you an estimate. Printing is generally not included in my cost.\r\n<h2>When and how is payment expected?</h2>\r\nA payment of 50% is required as soon as there is a signed contract for service. The remaining amount is due upon completion of your project. Payments are accepted through PayPal.\r\n<h2>Is a contract really necessary?</h2>\r\nYes. I begin work on a project when my proposal has been accepted and there is a signed contract for service.\r\n<h2>Are domain and hosting services included?</h2>\r\nNo, but I can make some recommendations for you. If you''re not sure what domains or hosting are, this short video explains what they are and why you need them.\r\n<h2>Is on-going maintenance included?</h2>\r\nNo, I provide support for 30 days after the site is approved and published. For an additional fee we can negotiate on-going maintenance or support.\r\n<h2>How long does it take to build a website?</h2>\r\nDepending on the project, about 30 days. If you''re contracting for graphic design services, that usually takes 7-10 days. The clock starts when there is a signed contract for service.\r\n<h2>What is the best way for us to stay in touch?</h2>\r\nIf you live in the Minneapolis area, I''d love to meet you face to face. If you''re not local then we can talk via Skype, Google chat, or on the telephone. We''ll use e-mail most of the time, but nothing beats a real-time conversation every once in a while.', 'Frequently Asked Questions', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2013-06-23 14:32:29', '2013-06-23 19:32:29', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?page_id=344', 0, 'page', '', 0),
