(582, 1, '2013-06-22 17:12:42', '2013-06-22 22:12:42', '<p class="portfolio-text">MTB Building &amp; Remodeling is the website for contractor Ben Losinski. Ben''s business is referral based and he wanted an online portfolio to show pictures of his work to potential clients. I talked to Ben at length about his business and philosophy for working with clients, vendors, and subcontractors, and also wrote the content for his About page.</p>\r\nBen''s site is a WordPress website that uses the ePhoto theme from Elegant Themes. The image gallery is managed by WordPress'' media library and uses the Lightbox Gallery plugin.\r\n\r\nVisit <a title="MTB Building &amp; Remodeling" href="http://mtbremodeling.com" target="_blank">MTB Building &amp; Remodeling</a>', 'MTB Building & Remodeling', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mtb-building-remodeling', '', '', '2014-04-27 23:28:11', '2014-04-28 04:28:11', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=582', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
