(562, 1, '2013-06-22 17:00:32', '2013-06-22 22:00:32', '<p class="portfolio-text">Happy Pet Sitters is a dog walking and pet care business in the northwest suburbs of Minneapolis. Owner Kirsten Trancheff had an outdated, static website that needed a redesign. Using the Sky theme from Elegant Themes, we made several changes to the typography and graphic images to personalize the design. We also added an image gallery of all the pets Kirsten and the Happy Pet Sitters team cares for, as well as information about services and rates.</p>\r\nOnce completed, Kirsten asked me if I could design some flyers that could be hung on doors while she is dog walking. Using the background images included with the Sky theme, I designed a doorhanger in Adobe InDesign and provided a PDF file that she can use to order her flyers from an online printer.\r\n\r\nVisit <a title="Happy Pet Sitters" href="http://happypetsitters.com" target="_blank">Happy Pet Sitters</a>', 'Happy Pet Sitters', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'happy-pet-sitters', '', '', '2014-04-27 23:28:11', '2014-04-28 04:28:11', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=562', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
