(1058, 1, '2013-11-27 18:42:08', '2013-11-28 00:42:08', 'Brad Kohler is a former UFC and MMA fighter who invented The Hitter System, a series of machines for training and working out. I designed his website at <a href="http://bradkohler.com" target="_blank">bradkohler.com</a>, I wrote the content for a <a href="http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bradfightmn/the-hitter-system?ref=live" target="_blank">Kickstarter</a> campaign, and I co-produced the project''s two videos.\r\n\r\n<figure><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/5syirmHbS4w" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></figure><figure><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/iZZOYRWJ5S0" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></figure>\r\n<h2>The Website</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>One Page – Static</li>\r\n	<li>HTML5/CSS/jQuery</li>\r\n	<li>Responsive</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Content</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Co-Wrote script for video and Kickstarter campaign</li>\r\n	<li>Copyedited script for web content</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The Video</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Recorded voice over with MXL990 USB Mic</li>\r\n	<li>Edited voice over with Adobe Soundbooth</li>\r\n</ul>', 'The Hitter System by Brad Kohler', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-hitter-system-by-brad-kohler', '', '', '2014-04-27 23:28:11', '2014-04-28 04:28:11', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=1058', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
