(1063, 1, '2013-11-27 19:05:26', '2013-11-28 01:05:26', 'Craig J. Hansen is the head of the Technical Communication graduate program at Metropolitan State University, and he is also a published author and musician. I was Dr. Hansen''s graduate assistant during the fall of 2013 when he hired me to make his personal website. I''ve also done quite a bit of photography and videography work for his performances with the <a href="http://cattailstringband.com" target="_blank">Cattail Moon Band</a> and the <a href="http://moretishans.com" target="_blank">More-Tishans</a>.\r\n\r\nHis website is a custom design and is fully responsive. Built with WordPress, it uses custom post types for the books on the home page, and for a video gallery of his concerts.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://craigjhansen.com" target="_blank">craigjhansen.com</a>', 'Craig J. Hansen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'craig-j-hansen', '', '', '2014-04-27 23:28:11', '2014-04-28 04:28:11', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=1063', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
