(1066, 1, '2013-11-27 19:21:52', '2013-11-28 01:21:52', 'Responsive Video Gallery is a personal project I developed and released into the public domain. In addition to the site, you can also find Responsive Video Gallery on <a href="https://github.com/angelajholden/responsivevideogallery" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.\r\n\r\nI decided to work on this when I needed a video gallery for a large website redesign being done with WordPress. I started by looking for WordPress plugins, but none of them did exactly want I was looking for, so I built it myself; first in HTML5, then in WordPress with Custom Post Types and Advanced Custom Fields. It also uses Jānis Skarnelis''s Fancybox jQuery plugin.\r\n\r\nThis video gallery is the perfect solution for both static and WordPress websites. It has a simple CSS grid that makes it responsive, and I provide the code for both CSS and SCSS. As you look at the websites in my portfolio, you''ll notice I''ve used it quite a bit in my personal projects and my client work.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://responsivevideogallery.com/" target="_blank">responsivevideogallery.com</a>', 'Responsive Video Gallery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'responsive-video-gallery', '', '', '2014-04-27 23:28:11', '2014-04-28 04:28:11', '', 0, 'http://angelajholden.com/ajh/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=1066', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
